#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:2
msgid "pytest-2.5.1: fixes and new home page styling"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:4
msgid ""
"pytest is a mature Python testing tool with more than 1000 tests against "
"itself, passing on many different interpreters and platforms."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:7
msgid ""
"The 2.5.1 release maintains the \"zero-reported-bugs\" promise by fixing the "
"three bugs reported since the last release a few days ago.  It also features "
"a new home page styling implemented by Tobias Bieniek, based on the flask "
"theme from Armin Ronacher:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:12
msgid "http://pytest.org"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:14
msgid ""
"If you have anything more to improve styling and docs, we'd be very happy to "
"merge further pull requests."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:17
msgid ""
"On the coding side, the release also contains a little enhancement to "
"fixture decorators allowing to directly influence generation of test ids, "
"thanks to Floris Bruynooghe.  Other thanks for helping with this release go "
"to Anatoly Bubenkoff and Ronny Pfannschmidt."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:22
msgid "As usual, you can upgrade from pypi via::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:24
msgid "pip install -U pytest"
msgstr "pip install -U pytest"

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:26
msgid ""
"have fun and a nice remaining \"bug-free\" time of the year :) holger krekel"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:30
msgid "2.5.1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:32
msgid "merge new documentation styling PR from Tobias Bieniek."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:34
msgid ""
"fix issue403: allow parametrize of multiple same-name functions within a "
"collection node.  Thanks Andreas Kloeckner and Alex Gaynor for reporting and "
"analysis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:38
msgid ""
"Allow parameterized fixtures to specify the ID of the parameters by adding "
"an ids argument to pytest.fixture() and pytest.yield_fixture(). Thanks "
"Floris Bruynooghe."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:42
msgid ""
"fix issue404 by always using the binary xml escape in the junitxml plugin.  "
"Thanks Ronny Pfannschmidt."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.5.1.rst:45
msgid ""
"fix issue407: fix addoption docstring to point to argparse instead of "
"optparse. Thanks Daniel D. Wright."
msgstr ""
